channel.title: 317 project pk-ownage
channel.description:
well as of today i decided to break away from my development team as seeing i always do all the work.
so today i am working on project pk-ownage v1
some features im adding or are added are below
[b]words like this mean im adding[/b] [u]words like this mean i want to add[/u] [s]words like this mean that i completed the goal[/s]
ok, so im starting on my 317 again.
but this time im making a twist...after creating 10 volumes of servers and 10 servers a volume...i think im ready to take on my big challenge
some features
[b]full pest control with waves full castlewars with scorings command to make members[/b]
[u]100% grand exchange feature all skills working maybe some quests[/u]
[s]working members places killer training working prayer full magic and range 1/5 skillcapes work like 508's npc dialouge with optionsfor players npcs cant walk through walls interface list in server file over 7k npc's[/s]
those are the features of my server...so yea...i will post pics when im done with a goal :)
that way you guys can see what im doing...then hopefully december 10th i will release the server.
~server percentage~
____________________________ | | | | |54% | | | | | | | --------------------------------
well i hope you guys look forward to this source...
